documentation:
Wraps a function that returns an effect with a new span for tracing.
*Example**

```ts
import { Effect } from "effect"

const getTodo = Effect.functionWithSpan({
body: (id: number) => Effect.succeed(`Got todo ${id}!`),
options: (id) => ({
name: `getTodo-${id}`,
attributes: { id }
})
})
```

